{"Name":"Chiku Mansions","ShortName":"Chiku Mansions","Description":"The Former Freehold Chiku Mansions site in District 15 has been acquired by Macly Group, with the previous site sitting on prime land close to popular schools such as Haig\u0027 Girls School and CHIJ Katong Convent, which adds to its residential appeal. It presents a strong potential for a new freehold boutique project tailored to owners \u0026 investors seeking a cozy lifestyle in a sought-after locale. ","StartUrl":"/","Display":"standalone","BackgroundColor":"#ffffff","ThemeColor":"#041e42","Orientation":"portrait","Icons":[{"Src":"https://rtdbookappointment.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/Bookappointment/Property/3c127f20-9f3f-4530-8212-b479f1a3c988","Sizes":"192x192","Type":"image/png"},{"Src":"https://rtdbookappointment.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/Bookappointment/Property/3c127f20-9f3f-4530-8212-b479f1a3c988","Sizes":"512x512","Type":"image/png"}]}